Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:03.86,Default,Ironwood,0,0,0,,Many have described these as uncertain times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:10.39,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,I'm trying to do what I think is best, but I really can't tell if what's best is what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.86,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:18.09,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,This whole city... it just seems awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:19.96,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,So, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.12,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Well we didn't come this far to fail now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:28.23,Default,Ironwood,0,0,0,,Until now, I believed it was impossible to truly turn the tide against Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.11,Default,Ironwood,0,0,0,,We find ourselves in a position of needing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.74,Default,Ironwood,0,0,0,,...a new approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:42.83,Default,Ironwood,0,0,0,,She will keep returning stronger and stronger, unless we destroy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:44.83,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Tell us how we can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.10,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,I was honestly expecting things to go a lot rougher.
